ll as compared to that of CaF2. Therefore, it has to be\nquestioned whether such narrow Ca(OH)2 and FAp layers really can act as\nprotective layers for the enamel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jun 2008 11:16:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-06-10"}
