elocities. Combining different indications and technics, we found\nthat 27% of the B-type stars are binaries. We also redetermined the age of\nNGC6611 found equal to 1.2--1.8 Myears in good agreement with the most recent\ndeterminations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jun 2008 11:32:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
